description.plain:
Quantavious Tavario Thomas (born December 17, 1992), better known by his stage name Young Nudy, is a rapper from Bouldercrest, Zone 6, East Atlanta, Georgia.

 His career started making waves in late 2015 after his feature on “Air It Out” by 21 Savage, his blood cousin. After that, he began forming a close connection with producer Pi'erre Bourne, and on October 2, 2016, Nudy dropped his Slimeball mixtape, which features predominant Pi'erre production.

Young Nudy’s career began picking up steam in the following years, with his SlimeBall 3 project being his first to chart on the Billboard 200, debuting at #146. Nudy’s largest song of his career came unexpectedly in early 2019 with the leak of the highly-anticipated “Pissy Pamper” featuring Playboi Carti.

songs.title: EA

description.plain:
“EA” is a song by Atlanta rapper Young Nudy enlisting frequent collaborator 21 Savage to represent East Atlanta in a hectic and fast-paced track, with a hard 808—courtesy of producer Pi'erre Bourne, another frequent collaborator of the duo.

EA leaked shortly before the official release of SlimeBall 2, originally without the guest appearance of 21 Savage. It was also initially believed to serve as the intro to the tape, rather than serving as the fourth track. Ultimately, EA ended up becoming one of Nudy’s most successful records to date.

EA gained traction yet another time in early 2022 on social-media platform TikTok, being used in various fast-paced photo compilations which subsequently boosted the popularity and traction of the record.

songs.title: Yeah Yeah

description.plain: Yeah Yeah is among Young Nudy’s best received tracks, featuring signature production from frequent collaborator Pi'erre Bourne. Throughout the 4:07 of synthy trap production, the artist boasts an impressive weapons arsonal, and raps about drugs, women, and his lack of trust. Originally posted to SoundCloud only, the track underwent revisions before it was released to DSPs where it would go on to bring the artist immense exposure and success.
